description:
Service Usage

This service is designed to be used by Client Search Portal only for the retrieval of FCC data. This includes data for each of the countries in the FCC and the levels of data captured. This service will continue to grow as the depth of the FCC data increases.

Service Usage

This service is designed to be used by Client Search Portal only for the retrieval of FCC data. This includes data for each of the countries in the FCC and the levels of data captured. This service will continue to grow as the depth of the FCC data increases.

Service Behaviour

This service is invoked only by CSP internally.

Service Variants

NA

Service Dependencies

NA

Service Composition

This service is only comprised of CDH data.

Service Flow

This service call is to CDH only.

Transformation

None

Service State Management Decisions

None
